Text: Friday feels different. Hope everyone has a good weekend coming up.
Started my morning with coffee before the sun came up. Those quiet minutes hit different.
Why does it feel like everyone decided to start their resolutions on the same day? The gym is packed.
Just discovered a podcast that explains things I thought I'd never understand.
Taking breaks is actually productive. Fight me.
Lunch thoughts: meal prepping on Sunday makes weekday me very happy.
Finally figured out a problem I've been stuck on for days.
Randomly ran into someone I haven't seen in years. Small towns are wild.
Checked something off my bucket list today. Not sharing details yet.
Weather has no idea what it's doing this week.
